Source: Each day you can collect a tonne of gold from the daily reward treasure chests. Join the group to get 3x more!

Source: Eggs can be found in each zone. With enough gold you can purchase your own pets to help you dig!
es-es: Hay huevos en cada área. Con suficiente oro puedes comprar mascotas que te ayuden a cavar.

Source: Every zone has a door you must buy before unlocking the next zone. You can get gold by digging for treasures.

pt-br: Cada área possui uma porta que voce deve desbloquear com ouro antes de avançar à próxima zona. Consiga ouro cavando tesouros.
Источник: В каждой зоне есть дверь, которую вы должны купить, прежде чем разблокировать следующую зону.  Вы можете получить золото, копая сокровища.

Source: Follow @NastaStudiosRB on Twitter for Epic Rewards!
